<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cheer-up">cheer up</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(使) 振作起来；(使) 高兴起来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She tried to cheer him up.
她努力让他高兴起来。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cheer up! Things will work out for the best.
高兴点儿！事情会圆满解决的。</p></div></div>